@node Main "Xtrings - Documentation"

                              'Xtrings' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Xtrings' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where 64 coloured shapes of
different types are placed on an 8 by 8 spaces game board. All
shapes are arranged in a 'clothesline' fashion, on a grid of
horizontal and vertical 'strings'. The idea is to move shapes by
clicking on the board's edges 'loops', so shapes make diagonal
alignements of at least 4 shapes of the same type. As 4 or more
shapes of the same type are aligned, they are then removed from
the board.

  Have fun!

